SUMMARY:Community Board Game Night
DESCRIPTION:Come down for board game night! Bring a simple game for others to play or play one that we have onsite. Hillsboro Downtown Station has Great food options from around the world\, and lots of great drinks on draft from your favorite local breweries. Come in early and enjoy happy hour from 2-5:30 and save $2 off any draft! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
