DESCRIPTION:Fridays at 10am\, Cameron Ford is hosting “Tiny Tunes”\, a weekly kids concert\, in the new and undiscovered living-room-style  show space (“the riff”) at b street records & vintage in downtown Milwaukie. Kicking off June 6\, this free\, family-friendly concert series is perfect for children ages 0-4 but all ages are welcome.
