SUMMARY:Tryon Open Classroom
DESCRIPTION:Join Friends of Tryon Creek in our Nature Classroom space. Open for parents and children visiting the park to come and experience nature-themed arts and crafts\, and learn about animals\, plants\, fungi\, and water. Kids can interact\, learn together\, and make new friends. \nMarch 20: Celebrate Spring Come and celebrate the new season of Spring at Tryon Creek. Join us for crafts in the classroom that honors the joy of Spring. Discover the plants and animals in the park! \nFree public event. No Registration is required. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/tryon-open-classroom/
