DESCRIPTION:Mr. Hoo rocks out at Mississippi Pizza every 1st and 3rd Friday at 5 p.m. After a long week\, nobody wants to figure out dinner\, entertain the kids and clean up. Come on out and Mr. Hoo and Mississippi Pizza will take care of everything. Yummy pizza for the whole family\, beverages (for kids and adults!) and rock n’ roll that’s fun for the whole family! Sometimes he’ll even have a guest or two (or 3)\, including his son Aidan. Only $5 per person.
